OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter teenage girl stabbed
OL,6,FA man has been charged with attempted
OL,7,Fmurder after a teenage girl was
OL,8,Fstabbed in the neck.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to Wood
OL,11,FStreet in Brierfield at 3:06pm on
OL,12,FFriday, 12 June, after a 17-year-old
OL,13,Fgirl suffered a stab wound to the back
OL,14,Fof her neck.
OL,16,FThe victim was rushed to hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment but officers have since
OL,18,Fconfirmed that her injuries are not
OL,19,Flife-threatening. She has been
OL,20,Fdischarged and is now "recovering at
OL,21,Fhome", Lancashire Police said.
