OL,3,CMan charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter teenage girl stabbed
OL,6,FA suspect was arrested nearby shortly
OL,7,Fafter the attack on suspicion of
OL,8,Fattempted murder.
OL,10,FJunaid Nawaz, who police say is
OL,11,FBritish-born of Pakistani heritage,
OL,12,Ffaces charges of attempted murder and
OL,13,Fpossession of a knife in a public
OL,14,Fplace.
OL,16,FThe 30-year-old, of Livingstone Walk,
OL,17,FBrierfield, has been remanded in
OL,18,Fcustody and is due to appear before
OL,19,FBlackburn Magistrates Court on Monday,
OL,20,F15 June.
